      <div>
        <head>Some transcribed text with subst errors</head>
        <p>... are all included. <del hand="#RG">It is</del>
          <subst><add>T</add></subst>the expressed</p>
        <p> that he and his Sister Miſs D —
        <lb/>who always lived with him, wd. be very
